Citation.sAbstract: The aim of this paper is to report experimental densities, excess molar enthalpies and refractive indexes of the ternary system (propyl  propanoate + hexane + toluene) and of the corresponding binary mixtures (propyl propanoate + toluene) and (hexane + toluene) at the  temperature 298.15 K and atmospheric pressure, over the whole composition range. Also, the excess molar volumes and the changes  the refractive index on mixing have been calculated from the measured data for all mixtures.
Citation.sTitle: Physical properties of (propyl propanoate + hexane + toluene) at 298.15 K
